 Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, in Paradise is a tent made of a hollowed pearl sixty miles wide, in each corner are families who do not see each other. The believers will roam freely between them. There are two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15205,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/21\/gold-silver-vessels-furniture\/","url_meta":{"origin":25473,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Using expensive vessels and silk furniture","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited us from eating and drinking out of golden or silver vessels. He prohibited us from wearing silk or brocade, or sitting upon anything made from them. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5499,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2067 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15256,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/remember-allah-eat-right-hand\/","url_meta":{"origin":25473,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Food: Remember Allah, eat with right hand","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Umar ibn Abi Salamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to me, \u201cYoung man, mention the name of Allah, e